## Section 2-1 Zoning Districts {#section-2-1}

The city is divided into zoning districts as shown on the official zoning map.

## Section 2-2 Permitted Uses {#section-2-2}

Permitted uses by district are listed in the use tables.

## Section 2-3 Special Use Permits {#section-2-3}

Special uses require review and approval by the zoning board.
